# User Tests

- Improve the usability of the app
- Usability vs UX
- A/B Testing
- Lean Startup Methodology

  - Usability testing is a technique for evaluating a product as a potential User


### Lean Startup Methodology
  - Create MVP (minimal viable product)
  - Test
  - Apply Changes
  - Repeat

  Smallest amount of building to prove a hypothesis


